												down = "[ScriptedGui.IsShown( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).AddScope( 'zz_selected_modifier', MakeScopeFlag(Scope.GetFlagKey) ).End)]"
												enabled = "[ScriptedGui.IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).AddScope( 'zz_selected_modifier', MakeScopeFlag(Scope.GetFlagKey) ).End)]"
												tooltip = "[ScriptedGui.BuildTooltip( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).AddScope( 'zz_selected_modifier', MakeScopeFlag(Scope.GetFlagKey) ).End)]"
											}	
										}
									}
									expand = {}
								}
							}
							expand = {}
							spacer = { size = { 0 10 } }
							vbox = {
								text_single = {
									align = left
									raw_text = "[GetPlayer.MakeScope.Var('zz_selected_modifier').GetFlagName]"
								}
							}
							vbox = {
								layoutpolicy_horizontal = expanding 
								layoutpolicy_vertical = expanding
								text_multi = {
									layoutpolicy_horizontal = expanding
									layoutpolicy_vertical = expanding
									minimumsize = { 300 300 }
									max_width = 300
									min_width = 300
									autoresize = yes
									text = "[Localize(Concatenate(GetPlayer.MakeScope.Var('zz_selected_modifier').GetFlagKey, '_desc' ))]"
								}
							}
							expand = {}
						}
						vbox = {
							layoutpolicy_horizontal = growing 
							layoutpolicy_vertical = growing
							max_width = 200
							spacer = { size = { 0 30 } }
							text_single = {
								Raw_Text = "Magic Regeants"
								fontsize = 24
								align = center
							}							
							spacer = { size = { 00 10 } }
							vbox = {
								button_standard = {
									datacontext = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_valyria_magic_item_craft_none')]"
									enabled = "[ScriptedGui.IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									down = "[ScriptedGui.IsShown( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									onclick = "[ScriptedGui.Execute( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									widget = {
										size = { 100 50 }
										text_single = {
											Raw_Text = "None"
											fontsize = 18
											resizeparent = yes
											align = center|nobaseline
											default_format = "#low"		
											margin = { 5 5 }
										}	
									}
									
								}
								button_standard = {
									datacontext = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_valyria_magic_item_craft_mages_power')]"
									enabled = "[ScriptedGui.IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									down = "[ScriptedGui.IsShown( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									onclick = "[ScriptedGui.Execute( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									widget = {
										size = { 100 50 }
										text_single = {
											Raw_Text = "Magic Power"
											fontsize = 18
											resizeparent = yes
											align = center|nobaseline
											default_format = "#low"		
											margin = { 5 5 }
										}	
									}
								}
								button_standard = {
									datacontext = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_valyria_magic_item_craft_dragonfire')]"
									enabled = "[ScriptedGui.IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									down = "[ScriptedGui.IsShown( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									onclick = "[ScriptedGui.Execute( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									widget = {
										size = { 100 50 }
										text_single = {
											Raw_Text = "Dragon Fire"
											fontsize = 18
											resizeparent = yes
											align = center|nobaseline
											default_format = "#low"		
											margin = { 5 5 }
										}	
									}
								}
								button_standard = {
									datacontext = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_valyria_magic_item_craft_human_sacrifice')]"
									enabled = "[ScriptedGui.IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									down = "[ScriptedGui.IsShown( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									onclick = "[ScriptedGui.Execute( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
									widget = {
										size = { 100 50 }
										text_single = {
											Raw_Text = "Human Sacrifice"
											fontsize = 18
											resizeparent = yes
											align = center|nobaseline
											default_format = "#low"		
											margin = { 5 5 }
										}	
									}
								}
								expand = {}
							}
							spacer = { size = { 00 200 } }
							vbox = {
								layoutpolicy_horizontal = expanding   layoutpolicy_vertical = expanding
								vbox = {
									layoutpolicy_horizontal = growing 
									layoutpolicy_vertical = growing
									text_single = {
										Raw_Text = "Current Cost"
										fontsize = 18
										min_width = 100
										align = center|nobaseline
										default_format = "#low"
									}							
									spacer = { size = { 0 10 } }						
									text_single = {
										raw_text = "[GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('zz_valyria_current_cost')|0] "
										min_width = 100
										align = center|nobaseline
										default_format = "#low"
									}
									expand = {}
								}
								spacer = { size = { 0 50 } }	
								vbox = {
									layoutpolicy_horizontal = expanding   layoutpolicy_vertical = expanding
									text_single = {
										Raw_Text = "Availaible Resources"
										fontsize = 18
										min_width = 100
										align = center|nobaseline
										default_format = "#low"
									}								
									spacer = { size = { 0 10 } }						
									text_single = {
										raw_text = "[GetPlayer.MakeScope.ScriptValue('zz_valyria_resources_current_spend')|0] "
										min_width = 100
										align = center|nobaseline
										default_format = "#low"
									}
									expand = {}
								}

							}
							spacer = { size = { 00 100 } }
							button_standard = {
								text_single = {
									minimumsize = { 200 38 }
									margin = { 15 15 }
									raw_text = "Craft Item"
									resizeparent = yes
									align = center|nobaseline
									default_format = "#low"								
								}
								datacontext = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_valyria_magic_item_craft')]"
								enabled = "[ScriptedGui.IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
								onclick = "[ScriptedGui.Execute( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
								tooltip = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_valyria_magic_craft_chance_ui').BuildTooltip( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End)]"
							}
							expand = {}
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		crafting_window_sword_selection_view = {}
		crafting_window_ring_selection_view = {}
	}
	type crafting_window_sword_selection_view = window {
		name = "crafting_window_sword_selection_view"
		movable = no
		layer = top
		parentanchor = top|hcenter
		position = { -500 20 }
		
		size = { 300 90% }

		using = Animation_ShowHide_Quick
		
		using = Window_Background_Subwindow
		visible = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_sword_selection_shown').IsValid( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End )]"
		vbox = {
			#set_parent_size_to_minimum = yes
			margin = { 4 4 }
			margin_bottom = 15
			margin_top= 15
			spacing = 15

			header_pattern = {
				layoutpolicy_horizontal = expanding

				blockoverride "header_text"
				{
					raw_text = "Select Sword"
				}

				blockoverride "button_close"
				{
					onclick = "[GetScriptedGui('zz_sword_selection_shown_close').Execute( GuiScope.SetRoot( GetPlayer.MakeScope ).End )]"
				}
			}
			expand = {}
			vbox = {
				layoutpolicy_vertical = expanding
				layoutpolicy_horizontal = expanding
				size = { 300 85%}
				scrollbox = {
					name = "mages_scrollarea"
